<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(gssize, gssize)
@returns(none)
def set_selection(start_pos, end_pos)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Selects the region of text between @start_pos and @end_pos.</p><p>This function changes the position of the cursor to match
@start_pos and the selection bound to match @end_pos.</p>

<table>
